Rog贸wko  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Kowale Oleckie, within Olecko County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south of Kowale Oleckie,  north of Olecko, and  east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
